text: MacOS Catalina (version 10.15) is the sixteenth major version of MacOS, Apple Inc.'s desktop operating system for Macintosh computers. It is the successor to macOS Mojave. MacOS Catalina was announced at WWDC 2019 on June 3, 2019. Catalina is the first version of macOS to support only 64-bit applications. It was released as a free update on October 7, 2019. As of August 2023, it is the most used version of macOS, at 91.16%. ==References== Category:MacOS
title: MacOS Catalina
